criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Healthy volunteers;

          -  Both genders;

          -  Age over 18 years;

          -  Clinical indication for PET-CT scan.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnant women;

          -  Patients who have lesions in the liver metabolically active whether primary or
             metastatic;

          -  Patients with movement difficulties.
